title: One Mo' Chance
overview: From the breakdown of his relationship with the mother of his children, to the death of his brother and partner Real," the last few years have been personally tough for Kamal Chance Givens. However, the original Stallionaire is now ready to get back on his horse to give love another shot. During Chance return to reality television we'll watch as he goes it alone to find the true love of his life in this new dating competition series.
